Annotation Interface Unsigned

@Documented @Retention(RUNTIME) @Target(METHOD) public @interface Unsigned
Annotation which indicates that a primitive column type be treated as an unsigned type. This affects the natural ordering of the column and its presentation by the row's toString method.
